               <item n="m_philcomment_old">&lt;h3&gt;Transliteration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;a2.&lt;/b&gt; According to [[TochSprR(B)2]]: 60 fn. 9 the reading &lt;i&gt;mäsketar&lt;/i&gt; should be corrected to &lt;i&gt;mäsketär&lt;/i&gt; in the transcription.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;a8.&lt;/b&gt; According to [[TochSprR(B)2]]: 61 fn. 9 the beginning of the line should be read as &lt;i&gt;moṣ&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Trancription&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;a1.&lt;/b&gt; Emendation according to [[TochSprR(B)2]]: 60 fn. 6.&lt;br&gt;
